          "returnType": "Vector[]",
          "description": "Returns the edge normals for this polygon. The returned array is cached and reused across calls — the same array reference is returned on consecutive calls when the polygon has not changed. The cache is invalidated automatically when setPoints, setPosition, set, or copy mutate the polygon. This matches the Circle.getNormals() and Sprite.getNormals() behaviour introduced in 0.6.19."
        },
